[02:15.93]First Gentleman	'Tis likely,
[02:17.11]	By all conjectures: first, Kildare's attainder,
[02:20.62]	Then deputy of Ireland; who removed,
[02:23.45]	Earl Surrey was sent thither, and in haste too,
