[02:31.38]	Was a deep envious one.
[02:33.38]First Gentleman	At his return
[02:34.76]	No doubt he will requite it. This is noted,
[02:38.07]	And generally, whoever the king favours,
[02:41.18]	The cardinal instantly will find employment,
[02:44.63]	And far enough from court too.
[02:47.11]Second Gentleman	All the commons
[02:48.63]	Hate him perniciously, and, o' my conscience,
