[04:43.60]	As I would be forgiven: I forgive all;
[04:46.56]	There cannot be those numberless offences
[04:49.87]	'Gainst me, that I cannot take peace with:
[04:53.05]	no black envy
[04:54.43]	Shall mark my grave. Commend me to his grace;
